On july 16, 2012
pickupsticks

You can only get a permanent link when you challenge someone BY NAME.
On the "who shall I fight?" page there's a box top right that says "Select an army base to infiltrate"
Put the name of the person you want to fight in here, and then you'll get a replay with a unique number in the URL instead of the BAT1/BAT2 type stuff.
Oh, and someone you challenge that way will be able to see that you fought them too.
Like so

Easiest way to do it is to highlight the name of the army from those on offer and drag it into the box... unless you have someone in particular in mind.

Xtremekiwihttp://juggling-act.minitroopers.com/...
Can someone please explain HOW my 4 recruits managed to miss that many times?

Sprinter and bad luck.
For all the shooting only 3 shots did not have aiming modifiers, the first shot and the last 2 shots.
The first shot was before your target moved (natural miss, bad luck) and the last 2 shots (which did hit) were after your target started aiming.
It's only when your target started the next action (aiming) that the previous action was 'actually' finished (moving). Even tho it will look like the trooper is just standing there, all other shots have an aiming modifier from a moving target with the sprinter skill.

Here is a shotgun missing a guy who 'looks' like he is just standing there doing nothing.
